  "description": "Legato sine strand in a trefoil knot where glide carries melodic lines through topological space. The knot type shifts the harmonic relationship between notes as you glide. LFO1 on braid depth at a very slow rate. Maximum reverb and chorus form an aetheric haze. Play slowly, hold notes long. This is the sound of topology as meditation.",
